  <h4>User Capacity Requirements</h4>
  <p>User capacity is calculated based on usable play area and age-appropriate space allocation.</p>

  <div class="formula-box">
    <strong>Formula:</strong> <code>Capacity = Usable Area ÷ Space per User</code>
    <br><em>Example: 20m² equipment allows 13 × 1.0m users (20 ÷ 1.5 = 13.3)</em>
  </div>

